commit.message:
Made `__{a}exit__` method args nullable. (#875)

This makes the methods compatible with typeshed's ABCs: https://github.com/python/typeshed/blob/5e9589dd75f8a5f39a38a2ed45f098ff62babc7f/stdlib/contextlib.pyi#L40-L54

Closes #874.

commit.message: Updated GitHub actions to their latest versions

tests: move to pytest-lazy-fixtures dep & mqtt update (#865)

This PR addresses failing tests due to pytest-lazy-fixture incompatibility with pytest v8, and breaking changes in paho.mqtt v2.

Replaces pytest-lazy-fixture with pytest-lazy-fixtures, and adjusts use of MQTT client to conform to new API.
